1 379.060. When such incorporators propose to form a
2 corporation for the purpose of doing business on the mutual
3 plan, the charter comprised in the declaration mentioned in
4 section 379.030 shall set forth:
5 (1) The name assumed by such corporation, and by which
6 it shall be known;
7 (2) The place where the principal office for the
8 transaction of its business shall be located;
9 (3) The specific kind or kinds of business which it
